
This is a basic chrome extension to access ones public profiles easily.

To try this: 
Step 1: 
	Download the complete repository 
Step 2:
	Open chrome://extensions in your chrome
Step 3:
	Make sure you have the Developer Mode turned ON
Step 4: 
	Click on Load unpacked and select the downloaded repository folder. 

Version 1.0.0 : 
First Cut with currently my profiles added. 


